Are you saying that because you have tried it, or because you think that
starting with a good set of parameters on the genome it would get better (or
stay as good)?

My prediction is that even if you started with the right parameters, it
would very quickly evolve bad parameters. That would be a good experiment.
Compare a set of good fixed parameters to evolving ones that start with
those same parameters.




